1.0.0.name: wordpress/auto-social-backlink-builder-free
1.0.0.description:
Auto Social Backlink Builder is a easy-to-use, powerful plugin that can help you publish your blog posts with backlink to all your configured social networks automatically. It's can save you a tremendous amount of time. Also, increasing your traffic, leads and sales.

Supported Networks Pinterest - Auto-Pin your blogpost's featured image to your Pinterest board. Delicious - Auto-submit bookmark to your account. Stumbleupon - Auto-submit bookmark to your account. more networks are coming soon ...

http://www.apponsite.com/wpextends/
